iament.uk/resources/1146307/answer","Biography information for Lord Agnew of Oulton","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1146307/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1146307/answer",,,,,"60","Education","Education","2019-09-25","Special Educational Needs: Hearing Impairment","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty's Government what action they will take to increase the employment of specialist teachers for deaf children by local authorities and schools.","false","Biography information for Lord Hunt of Kings Heath",,"Lord Hunt of Kings Heath","HL17802"
